<v-flex xs12 sm6 md4 d-flex>
  <v-select
    :items="marcas"
    label="Marca"
    box
    color="teal darken-3"
    v-model="marca"
    append-icon="fas fa-marker"
    @change="Selecionar(marca)"
    :rules="[() => !!marca || 'Este campo precisa ser selecionado!']"
  >
    <template slot="item" slot-scope="data">
      <v-flex xs10 sm10>
        <v-list-tile>
          <v-list-tile-content>
            <v-list-tile-title>{{data.item}}</v-list-tile-title>
          </v-list-tile-content>
        </v-list-tile>
      </v-flex>       
    </template>
  </v-select>
</v-flex>
